<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to <%= config.APP_NAME %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <img src="<%= baseUrl %>/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
    <h1>Welcome to <%= config.APP_NAME %>!</h1>
  </div>

  <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>

  <p>Thank you for joining our platform! We're excited to have you on board.</p>

  <p>Here are a few things you can do to get started:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Complete your profile</li>
    <li>Explore our documentation</li>
    <li>Join our community</li>
  </ul>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/getting-started" class="button">
      Get Started
    </a>
  </div>

  <p>
    If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team at
    <a href="mailto:<%= config.SUPPORT_EMAIL %>"><%= config.SUPPORT_EMAIL %></a>.
  </p>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>
      This email was sent to <%= email %>.<br>
      Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= config.APP_NAME %>. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 